WEBVTT

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:06.151
So, stepping down out of the bus,

00:00:06.151 --> 00:00:07.896
I headed back to the corner

00:00:07.896 --> 00:00:11.284
to head west en route to a braille training session.

00:00:11.284 --> 00:00:13.394
It was the winter of 2009,

00:00:13.394 --> 00:00:15.815
and I had been blind for about a year.

00:00:15.815 --> 00:00:17.948
Things were going pretty well.

00:00:17.948 --> 00:00:19.855
Safely reaching the other side,

00:00:19.855 --> 00:00:21.316
I turned to the left,

00:00:21.316 --> 00:00:23.920
pushed the auto-button for
the audible pedestrian signal,

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:25.844
and waited my turn.

00:00:25.844 --> 00:00:27.933
As it went off, I took off

00:00:27.933 --> 00:00:29.606
and safely got to the other side.

00:00:29.606 --> 00:00:31.702
Stepping onto the sidewalk,